headline: George Kurtz Becomes Co-Owner of Mercedes-AMG PETRONAS F1 Team Through Minority Acquisition in Toto Wolff Ownership Entity, Appointed Technology Advisor
summary: LAS VEGAS & BRACKLEY, England, November 20, 2025--The Mercedes-AMG PETRONAS F1 Team and George Kurtz, CEO and Founder of CrowdStrike, today announced that Kurtz has become a co-owner of the team and been appointed Technology Advisor.

headline: Mercedes F1 boss Toto Wolff sells a piece of his ownership stake to CrowdStrike CEO George Kurtz
summary: CrowdStrike CEO George Kurtz has acquired a minority stake in Mercedes-AMG Petronas F1 and will be a tech advisor to the motorsport team.
